cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.LG

This paper discusses the economics of privacy in personalization of online services, specifically focusing on web search. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), as it deals with privacy concerns. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY) as it discusses methods to personalize services based on user information. Additionally, it involves social and information networks (cs.SI) as it considers the preferences of users regarding privacy and utility. Finally, the paper uses optimization techniques (cs.LG) to find a near-optimal tradeoff between utility and privacy.
